dct_title_s: Rand McNally standard map of Virginia
dct_alternative_sm: Rand McNally new commercial atlas map of Virginia
dct_description_sm: Shows railroad index numbers, and electric and steamship lines overprinted in red.
"Rand McNally new commercial atlas map of Virginia."
Includes indexed list of Virginia railroads and inset map "Western portion of Virginia on same scale."
Indexes to counties, towns, and "Virginia auto roads" on verso.
